Build a React Todo List App in this beginner project tutorial. We will mainly use React hooks, so useEffect, useState, and useRef. You will be able to add, remove, edit, and mark complete/cross out the todo items. the mentor : Brian Design. link : youtu.be/E1E08i2UJGI